-- Currency's Gains May Hinder Australia's Budget Surplus Target, Review Says
-- B y   E l i s a b e t h   B e h r m a n n
-- 2010-10-06T20:01:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-06/currency-s-gains-may-hinder-australia-s-budget-surplus-target-review-says.html
Australia’s strong dollar and a
growing global currency imbalance are reducing business
competitiveness and might make it harder to achieve a budget
surplus by 2012-13, the Australian Financial Review reported,
citiing officials it didn’t name. Lower tax collection will
make budget forecasts more difficult, the officials said,
according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
